    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧀🧀 <strong>Billie’s Wheelie</strong> 🧀🧀</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for <strong>high-speed hamster chaos!</strong> 🐹💨<br>In this <strong>fast-paced adventure racing platformer</strong>, you take control of <strong>Billie, an adorable hamster on a mission to roll, race, and zoom through wild, dynamic tracks</strong>. Jump, dodge, and boost your way to <strong>victory</strong>, all while collecting <strong>cheese</strong> 🧀 and <strong>outplaying your opponents!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏁 <strong>ONLINE  FAST-PACED RACING ACTION! </strong>🏁<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180310/extras/937122c79df5f0c1eba55acf934ebca0.avif?t=1771706255\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180310/extras_big/937122c79df5f0c1eba55acf934ebca0.avif?t=1771706255 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speed through intense tracks</strong> designed to <strong>test your reflexes</strong>! With <strong>fluid movement, tricky obstacles, and crazy jumps</strong>! <strong>with 2 to 8 players online!</strong><br><strong>Master precise controls</strong> to drift, dodge, and boost your way past competitors!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨 <strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR HAMSTER!</strong> 🐹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180310/extras/f9726aa685bf74da72deb8e9014cf8d6.avif?t=1771706255\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180310/extras_big/f9726aa685bf74da72deb8e9014cf8d6.avif?t=1771706255 width=800 height=531 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your <strong>adorable</strong> <strong>hamster look</strong>, roll in a <strong>custom ball</strong>, and <strong>leave a trail mark </strong>as you speed through the tracks. and <strong>Celebrate your victories in style</strong> with <strong>hilarious victory emotes </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌍 <strong>EXPLORE DYNAMIC TRACKS!</strong> 🏁</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180310/extras/fd05d8582d6bd5d98328d2e1da8960d1.avif?t=1771706255\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180310/extras_big/fd05d8582d6bd5d98328d2e1da8960d1.avif?t=1771706255 width=800 height=402 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through <strong>stunning environments</strong>, from <strong>Candy World to  Space tracks</strong>, each packed with exciting surprises! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚡ <strong>SUN FLOWER SUPER POWER-UPS </strong> 🎢</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180310/extras/c69c0eadd2d468f77df4b360b50cb685.avif?t=1771706255\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180310/extras_big/c69c0eadd2d468f77df4b360b50cb685.avif?t=1771706255 width=800 height=207 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategize your way to victory</strong> with well-timed boosts, shields, and sneaky tricks to outplay the competition, By Unleashing <strong>crazy power-ups</strong> to <strong>boost past rivals, slow down opponents, and create total chaos </strong>on the track!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛣️ <strong>MORE CONTENT ON THE WAY! </strong>📌</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Career Mode,  Challenges &amp; MORE updates!</strong><br><strong>New levels, features, and surprises are coming!</strong> The race never stops in <strong>Billie’s Wheelie!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎉 <strong>ROLL, RACE &amp; CHEEEEEEEESE YOUR WAY TO VICTORY! </strong>🎉 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐹💨 <strong>Are you ready for a crazy hamster racing adventure?</strong> Jump in now and experience <strong>the thrill of speed and cheese-fueled fun!</strong> 🧀🏆</p>",
